Nigerian singer, Burna Boy has responded after many of his fans took to social media on Monday January 2, to blast him for keeping them waiting for seven hours at his concert in Lagos state on Sunday, January 1. One fan said he waited from 9pm on Jan. 1, 2023, and Burna arrived at about 4a.m. on Jan. 2. In a post shared on his Instatories this evening, Burna Boy apologized to his fans for how hectic the show was for them. He also blamed the organizers of the show for the delay. He further stated that he won’t be performing in Nigeria anytime soon, until his team is able to organise a show for him. Read what he wrote below.